    "chemicalDescription": [
      "r-Thermotoga Maritima Polypeptide-1 Oligopeptide-105 Oligopeptide-106 Hexapeptide-40 is a single chain recombinant fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli or Bacillus. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from r-Thermotoga Maritima Polypeptide-1, Oligopeptide-105, Oligopeptide-106 and {25967; Hexapeptide-40}. The fused peptide contains 431amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
